{"tid":2023571,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2018年女警開槍案　中槍男涉企圖傷人月底提堂","createTime":"2020-05-19T05:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T06:00:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3276feadfd7ccc5023303bec15928c8edb823f9a","tid":2023571,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:51:41.000Z","msg":"2018年11月7日早上約7時，港鐵深水埗站發生一宗警員開槍案，屬本港首宗女警開槍案。腹部中槍姓周(55歲)男子經手術取出彈頭後，情況一度危殆，其後獲准保釋候查。經調查，周男昨日(18日)被控兩項「企圖傷人」罪，案件將於本月29日於九龍城裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: 東網"},{"pid":"2965682971c49f44d0f34221d2ba4abceac6c3d9","tid":2023571,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"行得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b7ec3052a39d1e14a7b539f3baa25f418f2108","tid":2023571,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:53:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">光復香港，要你幫手！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【丫叉郵包案】<span style=\"color: orange;\">眾籌民事訴訟控告警方</span></strong><br />\n眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cMLSEJ&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=2600b10d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【612基金】<span style=\"color: orange;\">大量手足上庭，基金只剩幾三千萬！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://612fund.hk/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fdonate&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=d4ef3298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://612fund.hk/donate</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【星火】<span style=\"color: orange;\">以新模式運作，接受捐款！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ourhkworks.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ourhkworks.com&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=b01a834a\" data-auto-l